@node Appendix A TJM v11 Specification
@appendix Appendix A: TJM v1.1 Specification

The normative TJM v1.1 specification is maintained in @samp{docs/tjm-spec.md} in
the repository.  It defines:

@itemize
@item
The complete JSON schema for @samp{.tjm.json} files.
@item
The tick-based timing model and its relationship to real-time seconds.
@item
The edit overlay structure (@samp{edit} field on segments and words).
@item
The deterministic render contract that @samp{eve text-edit} implements.
@item
Migration paths from earlier TJM versions.
@end itemize

To read the specification, open @samp{docs/tjm-spec.md} in the repository or visit
the repository at @uref{https://github.com/behaghel/eve.el}.

